biography.placeOfBirth: Bon Thain, Celebes en Onderhoorigheden, Dutch East Indies [now Makassar, South Sulawesi, Indonesia]
biography.bio: Rina Hasyim was born on April 22, 1947 in Bon Thain, Celebes en Onderhoorigheden, Dutch East Indies. She is an actress, known for Bayi ajaib (1982), Tante garang (1983) and Godaan perempuan halus (1993).
biography.name: Rina Hasyim

biography.placeOfBirth: Serang, Bantam, Dutch East Indies [now Serang, Banten, Indonesia]
biography.bio: Muni Cader was born on February 2, 1932 in Serang, Bantam, Dutch East Indies. He was an actor, known for Bayi ajaib (1982), Revenge of the Ninja (1984) and Fatima (1983). He died on September 6, 2001 in Jakarta, Indonesia.
biography.name: Muni Cader

biography.placeOfBirth: Pontianak, Westerafdeeling van Borneo, Dutch East Indies [now Pontianak, West Kalimantan, Indonesia]
biography.bio: W.D. Mochtar was born on May 9, 1928 in Pontianak, Westerafdeeling van Borneo, Dutch East Indies as Wagino Dachrin Mochtar. He is an actor, known for La reine de la magie noire (1983), Satan's Slave (1982) and The Rebellious Woman (1982).
biography.name: W.D. Mochtar

biography.placeOfBirth: Magelang, Kedoe, Dutch East Indies [now Magelang, Central Java, Indonesia]
biography.bio: Wolly Sutinah was born on July 17, 1915 in Magelang, Kedoe, Dutch East Indies. She was an actress, known for Bayi ajaib (1982), Pedjuang (1961) and Manusia enam juta dollar (1981). She died on September 14, 1987 in Jakarta, Indonesia.
